dct_description_sm: Compiled from the latest United States Coast surveys ; published Oct., 1885 at the Hydrographic Office, under the authority of the Secretary of the Navy.
Depths shown by soundings, lines, and spot-shading (at low-water).
Tidal legend, list of lights abbreviations (with note), buoys legend.
Shows waterways, low-water areas, coastal cities.
